post_text:
Dear Cohasset Families,

We have been notified that poison ivy has been detected in areas around the Joseph Osgood and Deer Hill Schools. DPW will be treating those areas on Sunday, June 3, 2018. That means some areas will be off limits until Tuesday morning. This will not affect the recess play areas Monday or Tuesday. However, I ask that Sunday be off limits to all areas around the outside area of both schools.

Thank you,

Louise L. Demas, Superintendent
text:
Dear Cohasset Families,

We have been notified that poison ivy has been detected in areas around the Joseph Osgood and Deer Hill Schools. DPW will be treating those areas on Sunday, June 3, 2018. That means some areas will be off limits until Tuesday morning. This will not affect the recess play areas Monday or Tuesday. However, I ask that Sunday be off limits to all areas around the outside area of both schools.

Thank you,

Louise L. Demas, Superintendent
